excerpt.rendered: This is a work in progress map and will be updated continuously /—/ This is Medieval Minecraft City by McMeddon /—/ The GoalNr. 1: Build an alive City with Villager. My Goal with this to have a City that feels alive. I will use Villagers to populate the City. We will have housings, services and production buildings, where villagers will work and commute to.Nr. 2: Build a functional City with production lines We will create farms and productions for every item and at best we can create whole production lines that would supply the whole city.
